  fcron-2.0.0-r1.ebuild, files/digest-fcron-2.0.0-r1, ChangeLog :

  Resolved bug #4242 (ie. vim is no longer a dependency -- vim in turn
  depends on xfree86 which will surprise users when they emerge fcron)

